==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: For each part sewn, one part is reaped.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī fēn gēng yún, yī fēn shōu hùo

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[分]][[耕]][[耘]],[[一]][[分]][[收]][[获]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# You get out of it what you put into it.
# The more one works at something, the better the results.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[分]][[耕]][[耘]],[[一]][[分]][[收]][[穫]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

